   <text>
      <body>
         <!-- e caudata (ę) are regularized to a standard form ae/oe/e -->
         <div type="B">
            <div type="declamation" n="1">
               <p facs="#B147r">
                  <pb n="147r"/>
                  <lb break="yes"/>Incipiunt ex Calpurnio flacco excerpt<choice><orig>ę</orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>. Excerpta Decem
                  <lb break="yes"/>Rhetorum minorum. Uxor tyranni<add hand="#Bh1" place="above">ci</add>da
                  <lb break="yes"/><choice><abbr><supplied reason="missing-initial">Q</supplied>uinq:</abbr><expan><supplied reason="missing-initial">Q</supplied>uinq<ex>ue</ex></expan></choice> cum tyranno
                  proxim<choice><orig>ę</orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> famili<choice><orig>ę</orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> puniantur. <choice><abbr>Qu<choice><orig>ę</orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dā</abbr><expan>Qu<choice><orig>ę</orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>da<ex>m</ex></expan></choice>
                  <lb break="yes"/>qu<choice><orig>ę</orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> habebat duos filios et tyrannum virum tyrannici
                  <lb break="no"/>dum fecit. Pr<choice><orig>ę</orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>mio impunitatem liberis postulavit. Meruit.
                  <lb break="yes"/>Ex his alter occupavit arcem. At cum mater occidit petit alteri im
                  <lb break="no"/>punitatem. Contra dicitur. Occidam inquit. Quanta nobis
                  <lb break="yes"/>patienda sunt dum occiderit tyrannum f<choice><orig>ę</orig><reg>e</reg></choice>mina possit et <choice><abbr><hi rend="overline">mr</hi></abbr><expan>m<ex>ate</ex>r</expan></choice>
               </p>
               <p facs="#B147v">
                  <pb n="147v"/>
                  <lb break="yes"/>velit. Non possum mortem filii mei videre. Hoc est ergo quare <choice><abbr>illū</abbr><expan>illu<ex>m</ex></expan></choice>
                  <lb break="yes"/>velimus occidere. Pars altera.
                  <lb break="yes"/>Petit pr<choice><orig>ę</orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>mium non quod accipiat, sed quod accepit. </p>
            </div>
            <div type="declamation" n="12">
               <p facs="#B151r">
                  <pb n="151r"/>
                  <lb break="yes"/>Veneficii rea torqueatur donec conscios indicet. Amissa uxore ex <choice><abbr>q<hi rend="superscript">a</hi></abbr><expan>q<ex>u</ex>a</expan></choice>
                  <lb break="yes"/>habebat filium duxit alteram. Et de ea suscepit filiam. <choice><abbr>Adolever<hi rend="overline">t</hi></abbr><expan>Adolever<ex>un</ex>t</expan></choice>
                  <lb break="yes"/>ambo infantes repente ambiguis signis perit adolescens. Pater
                  <lb break="yes"/>uxorem accusavit et damnavit. Com <choice><abbr>torquere<hi rend="overline">t</hi></abbr><expan>torqueret<ex>ur</ex></expan></choice> filiam sibi <choice><abbr>cōsciā</abbr><expan>co<ex>n</ex>scia<ex>m</ex></expan></choice>
                  <lb break="yes"/>dixit. Petitur puella ex lege ad poenam. Adest ei <choice><abbr><hi rend="overline">pr</hi></abbr><expan>p<ex>ate</ex>r</expan></choice>. <add hand="#Bh2" place="margin">Pro filia</add>. Noverca filios
                  <lb break="yes"/><choice><abbr><hi rend="overline">nros</hi></abbr><expan>n<ex>ost</ex>ros</expan></choice> aut in simulatione persequitur aut veneno <choice><abbr><hi rend="overline">q</hi></abbr><expan>q<ex>uae</ex></expan></choice> scelus <choice><abbr>suū</abbr><expan>suu<ex>m</ex></expan></choice> <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr><expan>et</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>ī</abbr><expan>i<ex>n</ex></expan></choice> do
                  <lb break="no"/>mo venefice et in suppliciis docuit. Parricide adoleverunt ambo
                  <lb break="yes"/>sed minor filia et preter sexum multo fratre simplicior in uno <choice><abbr>utri⁹</abbr><expan>utri<ex>us</ex></expan></choice>
                  <lb break="yes"/>mentem videris cum periit adolescens et patri <subst><del>vindicatus est et</del><add hand="#Bh2" place="margin">venenum <choice><abbr>datū</abbr><expan>datu<ex>m</ex></expan></choice> est</add></subst> et
                  <lb break="yes"/>sorori. O noverca est alta crudelitas amasset et consciam putare
                  <lb break="no"/>mus. Proh nefas conscia dicitur cui <subst><del hand="#Bh1">pater</del><add hand="#Bh2" place="margin">frater</add></subst> periit. Cur <choice><abbr>post&#42839;<hi rend="superscript">a</hi></abbr><expan>postq<ex>uam</ex></expan></choice> ado
                  <lb break="no"/>levit puella est interemptus adolescens. Tam diu ergo fuit nover
                  <lb break="no"/>ce quieta crudelitas. <choice><abbr><hi rend="overline">&#42839;</hi></abbr><expan>q<ex>uam</ex></expan></choice> diu <choice><orig>ę</orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tas illius ad persusionem <choice><abbr>consciēti<choice><orig>ę</orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></abbr><expan>conscie<ex>n</ex>ti<choice><orig>ę</orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></expan></choice>
                  <lb break="yes"/>perveneri<del>n</del>t modum non habet iracundia mentiendi.
               </p>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div type="M">
            <div type="declamation" n="30">
               <p facs="#M14v">
                  <pb n="14v"/>
                  <lb/>Nepos, ex meretricio susceptus.
                  <lb/><num n="30">XXX</num>. Qui habebat filios, frugi <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr><expan>et</expan></choice> luxuriosum ab amore meretricis
                  <lb/>abdicavit. Abdicatus se ad <gap extent="1" unit="word" reason="blackened-out"/> meretricem contulit.
                  <lb/>Illic cum aegrotare coepi!et, misit ad patrem <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr><expan>et</expan></choice> com
                  <lb break="no"/>mendavit illi filim de meretrice susceptum, rogans
                  <lb/>ut eum in familiam recipiat et abiit. Vult illum senex
                  <lb/>in familiam recipere. Reus est alteri filio dementiae
                  <lb/>Contra patrem. <!-- hi rend allcaps? -->
                  <lb/>Necesse est me hodie in causa amplius dolere quam
                  <lb/>dicere. Pius est sine dubio filius qui in patre mentis
                  <lb/>errorem morbo potius a!ignat <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr><expan>et</expan></choice> fato quam moribus.
                  <lb/>Miseranda potius in <add hand="#Mh2" place="above">meo</add> patre <gap extent="1" unit="word" reason="blackened-out"/> quam accusanda de
                  <lb break="no"/>mentia est. Multum potest abdicatio cum timeretur
                  <lb/>post ex pudere iam liberius erratur. Vos interrogo
                  <lb/>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <pb n="15r"/>
                  <lb/>Iudices utrum sit sanus qui <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr><expan>et</expan></choice> suos abdicat <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr><expan>et</expan></choice> adoptat
                  <lb/>alienos. Adoptio sancta res est quidem quae beneficia
                  <lb/>naturae <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr><expan>et</expan></choice> iuris imitatur in quo puero nescio quid
                  <lb/>sit indignius utrum patris origo quod est dubia an
                  <lb/>matris origo quod certa est. Dixit ille suum filium
                  <lb/>dixit ut amator immo dixit ipse iam parum sanus.
               </p>
            </div>
         </div>
